graph LR
    ODH[Open Data Hub Operator<br/>v3.3.0]

    %% External Platform Dependencies - Required
    ODH -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25.0+<br/>OpenShift 4.19+]

    %% External Platform Dependencies - Optional
    ODH -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager Operator<br/>Latest]
    ODH -.->|job queuing| Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>Latest]
    ODH -.->|distributed training| LWS[LeaderWorkerSet Operator<br/>Latest]
    ODH -.->|observability| OpenTelemetry[OpenTelemetry Operator<br/>Latest]
    ODH -.->|tracing| Tempo[Tempo Operator<br/>Latest]
    ODH -.->|service mesh| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio/Sail]

    %% Core Kubernetes APIs
    ODH -->|operator mgmt| OLM[Operator Lifecycle Manager<br/>OLM]
    ODH -->|monitoring| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>monitoring.coreos.com]

    %% Internal ODH Components - Deployed by Operator
    subgraph Deployed["Components Deployed by ODH Operator"]
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI]
        KServe[KServe Operator<br/>Model Serving]
        DSP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>ML Orchestration]
        Ray[Kuberay Operator<br/>Distributed Compute]
        Training[Training Operator<br/>ML Training Jobs]
        ModelReg[Model Registry Operator<br/>Model Versioning]
        TrustyAI[TrustyAI Operator<br/>AI Explainability]
        Notebooks[Notebook Controller<br/>Jupyter Workbenches]
        ModelCtrl[Model Controller<br/>Model Orchestration]
        Feast[Feast Operator<br/>Feature Store]
        MLflow[MLflow Operator<br/>Experiment Tracking]
        Spark[Spark Operator<br/>Apache Spark]
        Trainer[Trainer<br/>Advanced Training]
        MaaS[Models as Service<br/>API Key Management]
    end

    ODH -->|deploys manifests| Dashboard
    ODH -->|deploys operator| KServe
    ODH -->|deploys operator| DSP
    ODH -->|deploys operator| Ray
    ODH -->|deploys operator| Training
    ODH -->|deploys operator| ModelReg
    ODH -->|deploys operator| TrustyAI
    ODH -->|deploys manifests| Notebooks
    ODH -->|deploys operator| ModelCtrl
    ODH -->|deploys operator| Feast
    ODH -->|deploys operator| MLflow
    ODH -->|deploys operator| Spark
    ODH -->|deploys operator| Trainer
    ODH -->|deploys manifests| MaaS

    %% Cloud Integrations
    subgraph Cloud["Cloud Platforms (Cloud Manager)"]
        Azure[Azure AKS<br/>cloudmanager.azure]
        CoreWeave[CoreWeave Kubernetes<br/>cloudmanager.coreweave]
    end

    ODH -->|cloud integration| Azure
    ODH -->|cloud integration| CoreWeave

    %% External Services
    ODH -->|image pulls| Registry[Container Registry<br/>Quay.io]

